OL,3,CCharity receives #1m to help with its
OL,4,Cfinancial shortfall
OL,6,FThe charity Live Borders will receive
OL,7,Fan additional #1million from Scottish
OL,8,FBorders Council.
OL,10,FThe authority approved the extra cash
OL,11,Fat a meeting today - it's the fifth
OL,12,Floan they've secured from the council
OL,13,Fin the last four years.
OL,15,FExternal consultants have recommended
OL,16,Fclosures and cuts across some of the
OL,17,Fleisure services the charity provides.
