OL,3,CCharity receives #1m to help with its
OL,4,Cfinancial shortfall
OL,6,FThe charity has made #250,000 in
OL,7,Fsavings, but still needs another
OL,8,F#250,000 to resolve its financial
OL,9,Fissues despite receiving a loan on 21
OL,10,FAugust 2025.
OL,12,FA public consultation is open until
OL,13,Fthe end of the month, with both Live
OL,14,FBorders and Scottish Borders Council
OL,15,Fwanting to hear views on the future of
OL,16,Fits service. The results of public
OL,17,Fengagement are expected to be released
OL,18,Fin October 2025.
