OL,4,Cfinancial shortfall
OL,6,FLive Borders Chief Executive Catriona
OL,7,FMcAllister says "there are a number of
OL,8,Fchallenges ahead".
OL,10,FShe said: "There is a changing mood in
OL,11,Fterms of the collaborative approach in
OL,12,Funderstanding the value of these
OL,13,Fservices to communities.
OL,15,F"The consultation has been well
OL,16,Fengaged with, and we are going to get
OL,17,Fsome rich data that may move the
OL,18,Fconversation a little bit from the
OL,19,Fcost of the services to the value they
OL,20,Fbring to the communities within the
OL,21,FScottish Borders."
