OL,4,Cfinancial shortfall
OL,6,FScottish Borders Council Leader Euan
OL,7,FJardine said: "It's going to take a
OL,8,Fwhile, but that's why we're doing a
OL,9,Fconsultation. That's why we're looking
OL,10,Fat the structure of Borders. We've got
OL,11,Fthe new Chief Executive and Chair.
OL,13,F"We're doing these things. It takes
OL,14,Ftime. We've got our budget coming up
OL,15,Fin six months. We've got time before
OL,16,Fthat. And I know six months goes past
OL,17,Fin a flash, especially in politics.
OL,18,FHowever, we're doing the right things
OL,19,Fand we're doing what we can.
