OL,6,F"We just need to make sure we're
OL,7,Fkeeping an eye on the ball here in
OL,8,Fterms of what our community has seen
OL,9,Fand what we can actually deliver, but
OL,10,Fat the same time, speak to communities
OL,11,Fand let them know we can't deliver the
OL,12,Fsame all the time.
OL,14,F"With a lot of technology coming in, a
OL,15,Flot of different habits are being
OL,16,Fformed after COVID. How do we get them
OL,17,Fback to using the facilities?"
